body.description: Ticonderoga has a tradition of fine quality writing instruments in the US for over 100 years. The exclusive graphite core features a proprietary formula focusing on graphite mined from carefully controlled sources to deliver extra smooth performance. Top-quality latex-free erasers remove marks completely without smudging. Premium wood harvested from responsibly managed sources provides smooth, even sharpening with minimal breakage. These pencils are pre-sharpened to save you time and hassle. Teachers prefer Ticonderoga for its dependability and craftmanship. When only the best will do, choose Ticonderoga brand pencils.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Kids loved it
reviews.reviewText: The Ticonderoga Wood-Cased Pencils, Pre-Sharpened, 2 HB Soft, Yellow, 30 Count, have been a fantastic addition to our household. These pencils have quickly become a favorite among the kids in our family. Their bright yellow color and pre-sharpened tips make them appealing and convenient for both schoolwork and creative projects.What sets these pencils apart is their smooth and consistent performance. The 2 HB soft lead provides just the right balance between darkness and precision, making them suitable for various tasks. Whether it's writing, drawing, or shading, these pencils deliver excellent results every time.Furthermore, the durability of these pencils is impressive. They withstand the daily wear and tear of active young learners. We've noticed that they don't break easily, which means less frustration for the kids and fewer interruptions during their activities.In terms of value, the 30-count pack ensures that we always have plenty of these reliable pencils on hand. It's a practical choice for families with multiple children or for teachers who want to stock up for their classrooms.Overall, the Ticonderoga Wood-Cased Pencils have won us over with their quality, reliability, and kid-friendly design. We highly recommend them to anyone in need of top-notch pencils for their little ones.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ticonderoga Pencils: A Golden Standard in Writing Excellence!
reviews.reviewText: I recently got my hands on the Ticonderoga Graphite Pencils, and they are nothing short of amazing. No more eraser mishaps!Kid-Friendly Assurance: If you have little ones around, you'll be pleased to know that these pencils are PMA-certified and non-toxic. Being a part of the Dixon Ticonderoga family of products, they have a long-standing history of delivering quality. From artists to students, they cater to everyone's needs.In conclusion, Ticonderoga Graphite Pencils have won me with their superb performance, sustainability, and peace of mind. They've become my go-to choice for all my writing needs. If you're in the market for top-notch pencils, do yourself a favor and grab a pack of these beauties – you won't be disappointed!

Not only do you get a generous count of 30 pencils, but they also come pre-sharpened, which is a huge time-saver. The classic yellow color and the iconic Ticonderoga branding make these pencils easily recognizable and a staple for any stationery collection.I’m pleased to say that these pencils are exactly as advertised. The quality and performance live up to the Ticonderoga reputation. They sharpen nicely, write smoothly, and the lead doesn’t smudge easily. Whether you’re a student, professional, or artist, these pencils are versatile and reliable.
